取突擊搜查行動。原本執政的共和黨白宮新聞發言人說，拜登及黨內其他高層人士被帶走。特朗普呼籲支持者不要衝動，並要依法行事。<br />\n<br />\n發言人又說，根據目前發生的情況，不得不猜測軍方發動政變。<br />\n<br />\n軍方清晨的行動之後，美國的通訊受阻，幾個流動電話網絡中斷，互聯網服務亦受嚴重干擾，首都華盛頓和主要城市的電話都不通。國營電視台在社交網站說，由於技術問題，不能照常廣播。<br />\n<br />\n主要城市和華盛頓的市政廳外有士兵部署，軍車停在附近。<br />\n<br />\n侵本身要做GE事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2389564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2389564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573401-20210201.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573401-20210201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQlwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=da30b694\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573401-20210201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3f92c819\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573401-20210201.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T23:39:35.000Z","msg":"你呢d 廢文，一定比左報大做文章，順勢攪埋連登專做假新聞<br />\n<br />\n有無腦ga"},{"pid":"1adbccce6178326be735d8ddd0550256ff9b4529","tid":2390801,"uid":354403,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T23:39:57.000Z","msg":"Fake news<br />\n<br />\nBlock"},{"pid":"95de940ad8d0ee88c58091a682eefe18195d087f","tid":2390801,"uid":6058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"41e08e0e96b6caee077edef540ee36f2e01908e8","tid":2390801,"uid":61832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T23:26:06.000Z","msg":"用下你個閪腦去思考下有乜可以講有乜唔可以講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T23:40:28.000Z","msg":"入去坐低大把時間俾佢諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最撚憎假膠<br />\n冇假膠<br />\n五毛唔會咁放肆"},{"pid":"a74a1ae2e5c7bb24d0f871c64fac31d63e2ed474","tid":2390801,"uid":34241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T23:50:45.000Z",